{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2019-09-01-git_upstream/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"박준우 블로그"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"45dc778b-f32f-544f-9c59-2ee63d9c01f3","excerpt":"오픈소스를 Fork해서 만지작거리는 일이 많은데요. 이렇게 만지작거리는 사이에 원본 저장소가 업데이트되는 일이 빈번해서 곤란한 경우가 가끔 있습니다. Fork를 삭제하고 다시 Fork했던 지난날의 모습을 부끄러워하고 반성하며, Fork…","html":"<p>오픈소스를 Fork해서 만지작거리는 일이 많은데요.</p>\n<p>이렇게 만지작거리는 사이에 원본 저장소가 업데이트되는 일이 빈번해서 곤란한 경우가 가끔 있습니다.</p>\n<p>Fork를 삭제하고 다시 Fork했던 지난날의 모습을 부끄러워하고 반성하며,</p>\n<p>Fork받은 저장소를 최신 원본으로 동기화하는 방법을 정리해보려고 합니다.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>1.우선 현재 저장소의 원격 주소를 확인합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ git remote -v\n\norigin  https://github.com/USERNAME/FORK_REPO.git (fetch)\norigin  https://github.com/USERNAME/FORK_REPO.git (push)</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ecd199ec3caf3aafd3d640659850b614/906b5/fork1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 10.759493670886075%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAIAAADXZGvcAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAZUlEQVQI1w3LSw7CMAwA0V4lgD+xHccJbSEqgvvfCktvMZvZUGFN+MTtGnDF/XvweK/XsF/QfrgG9ibepDIyJQB4EEEqpWzC2F2RMNxEODtaNeXots7xjDa7zbBwHd2SCmW71Zz/AMUUvdhq94IAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"fork1\"\n        title=\"fork1\"\n        src=\"/static/ecd199ec3caf3aafd3d640659850b614/f058b/fork1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ecd199ec3caf3aafd3d640659850b614/c26ae/fork1.png 158w,\n/static/ecd199ec3caf3aafd3d640659850b614/6bdcf/fork1.png 315w,\n/static/ecd199ec3caf3aafd3d640659850b614/f058b/fork1.png 630w,\n/static/ecd199ec3caf3aafd3d640659850b614/40601/fork1.png 945w,\n/static/ecd199ec3caf3aafd3d640659850b614/906b5/fork1.png 950w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>2.원본 저장소의 원격 주소를 추가합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ git remote add upstream https://github.com/ORIGINAL_OWNER/ORIGINAL_REPO.git</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/45ad390dd1fe3519c47d38240cd73dcc/a83dd/fork2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 2.5316455696202533%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAABCAIAAABR8BlyAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAPUlEQVQI1xXKwRHAIAhEUQvJ1YTAsoAzdmD/NanX939b9fn0Xo+pjARMkkZohdE1XIm/AiLv8RF3OJi8aQNBggp5sge0kAAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"fork2\"\n        title=\"fork2\"\n        src=\"/static/45ad390dd1fe3519c47d38240cd73dcc/f058b/fork2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/45ad390dd1fe3519c47d38240cd73dcc/c26ae/fork2.png 158w,\n/static/45ad390dd1fe3519c47d38240cd73dcc/6bdcf/fork2.png 315w,\n/static/45ad390dd1fe3519c47d38240cd73dcc/f058b/fork2.png 630w,\n/static/45ad390dd1fe3519c47d38240cd73dcc/40601/fork2.png 945w,\n/static/45ad390dd1fe3519c47d38240cd73dcc/78612/fork2.png 1260w,\n/static/45ad390dd1fe3519c47d38240cd73dcc/a83dd/fork2.png 1482w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>3.원본 저장소의 원격 주소가 잘 추가되었는지 확인합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ git remote -v\n\norigin  https://github.com/USERNAME/FORK_REPO.git (fetch)\norigin  https://github.com/USERNAME/FORK_REPO.git (push)\nupstream  https://github.com/ORIGINAL_OWNER/ORIGINAL_REPO.git (fetch)\nupstream  https://github.com/ORIGINAL_OWNER/ORIGINAL_REPO.git (push)</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c19586444d98eb5e13457ff5dfac4383/99661/fork3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 16.455696202531648%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAIAAAAcOLh5AAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAhElEQVQI1x2OgQ7DIAhE+ydth4oinFZbk+3/P2xsLxcCJHewFY0LtCwsxPfFmPfU/LmkT9HKpiVzYk4phRhD5kj02g/ndDaoALWU7AA6mpjJHFgDo+szMLs9/7636pVT9CAi+pmr8NWEUziPHZph2kxcqgUoHdXlo7/gZhWukn0TAvnxL74vHeWCuh+/AAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"fork3\"\n        title=\"fork3\"\n        src=\"/static/c19586444d98eb5e13457ff5dfac4383/f058b/fork3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c19586444d98eb5e13457ff5dfac4383/c26ae/fork3.png 158w,\n/static/c19586444d98eb5e13457ff5dfac4383/6bdcf/fork3.png 315w,\n/static/c19586444d98eb5e13457ff5dfac4383/f058b/fork3.png 630w,\n/static/c19586444d98eb5e13457ff5dfac4383/40601/fork3.png 945w,\n/static/c19586444d98eb5e13457ff5dfac4383/99661/fork3.png 1098w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>4.원본을 fetch합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ git fetch upstream\n\nremote: Enumerating objects: 134, done.\nremote: Counting objects: 100% (134/134), done.\nremote: Compressing objects: 100% (23/23), done.\nremote: Total 191 (delta 117), reused 123 (delta 111), pack-reused 57\nReceiving objects: 100% (191/191), 88.60 KiB | 257.00 KiB/s, done.\nResolving deltas: 100% (117/117), completed with 4 local objects.\nFrom https://github.com/ORIGINAL_OWNER/ORIGINAL_REPO\n * [new branch]      master     -&gt; upstream/master</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bd03bc5142853bf02676fe37bf4e1fe8/7bf07/fork4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 29.746835443037973%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"fork4\"\n        title=\"fork4\"\n        src=\"/static/bd03bc5142853bf02676fe37bf4e1fe8/f058b/fork4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bd03bc5142853bf02676fe37bf4e1fe8/c26ae/fork4.png 158w,\n/static/bd03bc5142853bf02676fe37bf4e1fe8/6bdcf/fork4.png 315w,\n/static/bd03bc5142853bf02676fe37bf4e1fe8/f058b/fork4.png 630w,\n/static/bd03bc5142853bf02676fe37bf4e1fe8/40601/fork4.png 945w,\n/static/bd03bc5142853bf02676fe37bf4e1fe8/7bf07/fork4.png 1128w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>5.upstream/master를 나의 master에 합치기</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ git merge upstream/master\n\nUpdating 3b10450..0a9aada\nFast-forward\n README.md         | 858 +-------\n db.yml            | 240 ++++--\n db_community.yml  |  35 ++-\n db_opensource.yml |  22 ++\n 4 files changed, 274 insertions(+), 881 deletions(-)</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ac6a488449fc1249aa6c03238eaddb67/daed9/fork5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 19.62025316455696%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAECAIAAAABPYjBAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAg0lEQVQI13WNSw6DQAxDuQnJON+BgRboopv2/rfq0F2lYj15YSX2sN3ttel71+cx7cf+SGjCXcMt4gQAX2hYWm1tgihzyVAGSyEBoRCYCndn4R7/0JPSn9uUa0tTEcE8hwTBRhhBRybi79FfzuWavi51u81T9Vo901zVTcMsw3ojX+sDzZ8iaLlsf2QAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"fork5\"\n        title=\"fork5\"\n        src=\"/static/ac6a488449fc1249aa6c03238eaddb67/f058b/fork5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ac6a488449fc1249aa6c03238eaddb67/c26ae/fork5.png 158w,\n/static/ac6a488449fc1249aa6c03238eaddb67/6bdcf/fork5.png 315w,\n/static/ac6a488449fc1249aa6c03238eaddb67/f058b/fork5.png 630w,\n/static/ac6a488449fc1249aa6c03238eaddb67/40601/fork5.png 945w,\n/static/ac6a488449fc1249aa6c03238eaddb67/78612/fork5.png 1260w,\n/static/ac6a488449fc1249aa6c03238eaddb67/daed9/fork5.png 1426w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>6.나의 원격저장소에 push합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ git push origin master\n\nTotal 0 (delta 0), reused 0 (delta 0)\nTo https://github.com/USERNAME/FORK_REPO.git\n   3b10450..0a9aada  master -&gt; master</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d1e907bbc17bae23bc274636360c09de/898f6/fork6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 17.088607594936708%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAIAAAAcOLh5AAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAjElEQVQI1x2NWQ6DMAxEuQmFLHbsOHESBOqqcv9L1XQ0mr83bwKFe4/n8J8R3j2cw71GrMdj3/pXw1OpbEziM6XgXcIYg0cIlMC5daIIIpyYMCWRzDkjYiHomttQVVGhVjInMJLQFuxgnm+WaVkXyXhstRWukvZRWmW7uuBqgjiURzMxmNB6yaNf/vkBIQkeQp9T45UAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"fork6\"\n        title=\"fork6\"\n        src=\"/static/d1e907bbc17bae23bc274636360c09de/f058b/fork6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d1e907bbc17bae23bc274636360c09de/c26ae/fork6.png 158w,\n/static/d1e907bbc17bae23bc274636360c09de/6bdcf/fork6.png 315w,\n/static/d1e907bbc17bae23bc274636360c09de/f058b/fork6.png 630w,\n/static/d1e907bbc17bae23bc274636360c09de/898f6/fork6.png 798w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"fork한 저장소를 최신 원본과 동기화시키기","date":"September 01, 2019","description":"Fork받은 저장소를 최신 원본으로 동기화하는 방법을 정리해보려고 합니다."}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2019-08-29-BEM/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"BEM이란?"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2019-09-03-git이저장하는방식/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"git이 저장하는 방식"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"45dc778b-f32f-544f-9c59-2ee63d9c01f3","previousPostId":"b356963d-8da3-53b1-bed3-d8955b487edb","nextPostId":"1c91c5a3-6cd1-54fe-ac6c-9d44b6ba8338"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","916993862"]}